      "id": "PopularPost43570",
      "post_content": "Hey there, [Parallax Wave](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Parallax Wave) and [Parallax Tide](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Parallax Tide)! I heard you like to leave the battlefield at instant speed.  \n  \n@Donovan\\_Fabian:  \nUnfortunately, [Rancor](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rancor) can't be replayed on your opponent's turn. You'd need something like [Vedalken Orrery](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vedalken Orrery) to pull it off effectively. Plus, that would require a four-color deck. Maybe [Brilliant Halo](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brilliant Halo), [Despondency](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Despondency), [Launch](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Launch), or [Spirit Loop](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spirit Loop) would be easier.",
      "posted_by": "Ragamander",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost43570\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Hey there, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Parallax Wave\">Parallax Wave</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Parallax Tide\">Parallax Tide</a>!  I heard you like to leave the battlefield at instant speed.<br/><br/>@Donovan_Fabian:<br/>Unfortunately, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Rancor\">Rancor</a> can't be replayed on your opponent's turn.  You'd need something like <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vedalken Orrery\">Vedalken Orrery</a> to pull it off effectively.  Plus, that would require a four-color deck.  Maybe <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brilliant Halo\">Brilliant Halo</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Despondency\">Despondency</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Launch\">Launch</a>, or <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spirit Loop\">Spirit Loop</a> would be easier.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy13722\">Ragamander</span>\r\n                                (11/14/2011 3